Package org.jdom2.jaxb

This package contains experimental classes from the JDOM development branch that are utilized by XFlat.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JDOMNamespaceContext
    A Read-Only NamespaceContext that describes namespaces found in a JDOM node.
    JDOMStreamReader
    An XMLStreamReader implementation that reads the XML document out of a JDOM Document.
    JDOMStreamWriter
    An XMLStreamWriter implementation that writes XML data to a new JDOM Document.
    NamespaceStack
    A high-performance stack for processing those Namespaces that are introduced or are in-scope at a point in an Element hierarchy.

Package org.jdom2.jaxb Description

This package contains experimental classes from the JDOM development branch that are utilized by XFlat. Future versions of XFlat will use a newer version of JDOM that contains these classes.
